You were in on numerous occasions, is that right? Yes, drunk charges and stuff like that.

15:24.600 --> 15:29.640
My father actually took me in. Your father actually took you in? How do you mean?

15:30.280 --> 15:33.560
Well, my father, well, he don't drink and he don't smoke and stuff, see?

15:34.520 --> 15:39.240
And so I'm one of the, well, out of my whole family, I'm the only one, me and my cousin

15:39.240 --> 15:44.920
about the only ones that have been arrested, smoking, drank, see? And you only lived with your father

15:44.920 --> 15:48.200
a short time about a year or something. Yeah, about a year or two once.

15:49.240 --> 15:54.280
And well, my father's kind of strict on it, saying, you don't like it. So I used to do it anyway.

15:54.280 --> 15:58.440
I didn't care. It was not a business, it was mine. Since he never did anything for me,

15:58.440 --> 16:02.600
I think, what should I do something for him? When he hadn't taken care of you, felt you owed him

16:02.600 --> 16:07.000
nothing and you didn't expect him to give you anything in return, is that right? That's true.

16:07.880 --> 16:11.800
Well, after a while, it kind of got to be a habit. I was hanging around with a bunch of

16:12.520 --> 16:18.040
hoodlums out here. We got together every night, you know, or something. The God messed up,

